he normalized energy use in kWh/m<span><sup>2</sup></span>/yr.</p><p>E<span><sub>use_ref</sub></span> \tis GSAS benchmark for the energy use.  It is the reference energy of the notional building for a specific building type in kWh/m<span><sup>2</sup></span>/yr.</p><p><br/>The <span>criterion level</span> is established based on the result of the EPC<span><sub>use</sub></span>.</p>", display_weight: 3)
